---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — TradingToolsHub"
  description="TradingToolsHub privacy policy. How we collect, use, and protect your personal information."
  canonical="https://tradingtoolshub.com/privacy/"
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <nav class="text-sm text-muted mb-8">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-text transition-colors">Home</a>
      <span class="mx-2">/</span>
      <span class="text-text">Privacy Policy</span>
    </nav>

    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-text mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-muted mb-10">Last updated: March 9, 2026</p>

    <div class="space-y-8 text-muted leading-relaxed text-[15px]">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">Who We Are</h2>
        <p>TradingToolsHub (<a href="https://tradingtoolshub.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">tradingtoolshub.com</a>) is an independent trading tools comparison directory operated by Cosmic Phoenix LLC, a Wyoming limited liability company. Our mission is to help traders find the right tools through honest, data-driven reviews and comparisons.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">Information We Collect</h2>
        <h3 class="font-medium text-text mt-4 mb-2">Information you provide</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
          <li><strong class="text-text">Email address</strong> — if you subscribe to our newsletter via the signup form</li>
        </ul>
        <h3 class="font-medium text-text mt-4 mb-2">Information collected automatically</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
          <li><strong class="text-text">Analytics data</strong> — We use Google Analytics 4 (GA4) to understand how visitors use the site. This includes pages visited, time on site, device type, approximate geographic location, and referral source. GA4 does not collect personally identifiable information by default.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-text">Server logs</strong> — Standard web server logs may record your IP address, browser type, and pages requested. These are retained for security and debugging purposes only.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
          <li>To send our newsletter if you opted in (you can unsubscribe at any time)</li>
          <li>To understand how visitors use the site and improve our content</li>
          <li>To maintain site security and prevent abuse</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3">We do <strong class="text-text">not</strong> sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">Cookies and Tracking</h2>
        <p>We use cookies set by Google Analytics to measure site usage. These are first-party analytics cookies and do not track you across other websites. You can opt out of Google Analytics by installing the <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-primary hover:underline">Google Analytics Opt-out Browser Add-on</a>.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">Affiliate Links</h2>
        <p>Some links on TradingToolsHub are affiliate links. When you click on these links and make a purchase or sign up, we may earn a commission at no additional cost to you. Affiliate partners may use their own cookies to track referrals. Please review the privacy policies of any service you sign up for through our links. For more details, see our <a href="/affiliate-disclosure/" class="text-primary hover:underline">Affiliate Disclosure</a>.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">Third-Party Services</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
          <li><strong class="text-text">Google Analytics 4</strong> — Website analytics (<a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-primary hover:underline">Google Privacy Policy</a>)</li>
          <li><strong class="text-text">EmailOctopus</strong> — Newsletter delivery (<a href="https://emailoctopus.com/legal/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-primary hover:underline">EmailOctopus Privacy Policy</a>)</li>
          <li><strong class="text-text">Vercel</strong> — Website hosting (<a href="https://vercel.com/legal/privacy-policy" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-primary hover:underline">Vercel Privacy Policy</a>)</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">Data Retention</h2>
        <p>Newsletter subscriber email addresses are retained until you unsubscribe. Analytics data is retained according to Google Analytics' default retention settings (14 months). Server logs are retained for up to 90 days.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 mt-2">
          <li>Unsubscribe from our newsletter at any time (link in every email)</li>
          <li>Request a copy of any personal data we hold about you</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your personal data</li>
          <li>Opt out of analytics tracking</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3">To exercise any of these rights, email us at <a href="mailto:editorial@tradingtoolshub.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">editorial@tradingtoolshub.com</a>.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>TradingToolsHub is not intended for children under 18. We do not knowingly collect personal information from minors. Trading and financial products involve risk and are not suitable for minors.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date. Continued use of the site after changes constitutes acceptance of the revised policy.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">Contact</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy, contact us at <a href="mailto:editorial@tradingtoolshub.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">editorial@tradingtoolshub.com</a>.</p>
        <p class="mt-2">Cosmic Phoenix LLC<br />Wyoming, USA</p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
